==年齡爭議==
早於[[北京2008奥运会|北京2008奥运会]]開幕前，已有外國媒體報導她的年齡可能不足16歲<ref>{{cite web | language=en | publisher=纽约时报 | title=Records Say Chinese Gymnasts May Be Under Age | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/07/27/sports/olympics/27gymnasts.html?_r=1&hp | author=By JERÉ LONGMAN and JULIET MACUR | date=July 27, 2008 | accessdate=2008-08-24 | archive-date=2019-03-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190312194345/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/07/27/sports/olympics/27gymnasts.html?_r=1&hp }}</ref><ref>{{cite web| language=zh-hant| publisher=自由電子報| title=美媒質疑 中國體操選手年齡造假| url=http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2008/new/jul/29/today-sp1.htm| author=| date=| accessdate=2008-08-24| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080824233615/http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2008/new/jul/29/today-sp1.htm| archivedate=2008-08-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| language=zh-hant| publisher=世界日報| title=何可欣不足齡? 金牌恐不保 新華社去年報導她13歲 楊伊琳、江鈺源也受質疑 當局堅稱3人已滿16歲| url=http://www.worldjournal.com/wj-ch-news.php?nt_seq_id=1759781| author=| date=| accessdate=2008-08-24| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080824060123/http://www.worldjournal.com/wj-ch-news.php?nt_seq_id=1759781| archivedate=2008-08-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language=en | publisher=NBCOlympics.com | title=Age of Chinese gymnast under scrutiny | url=http://www.nbcolympics.com/gymnastics/news/newsid=213588.html?_source=rss&cid= | author= | date=August 14, 2008 | accessdate=2008-08-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161215125535/http://www.nbcolympics.com/gymnastics/news/newsid=213588.html?_source=rss&cid= | archive-date=2016-12-15 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>，質疑她的參賽資格。為了釋疑，[[国际体操联合会|国际体操联合会]]遂要求中国提供更多证据，以证明所有中国女體操选手均已達到最低參賽年龄<ref>{{cite web | language=zh | publisher=BBC中文网 | title=国际体操联合会调查中国选手年龄 | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/simp/hi/newsid_7570000/newsid_7578100/7578168.stm | author= | date=2008年8月23日 | accessdate=2008-08-24 | archive-date=2008-08-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080828063517/http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/simp/hi/newsid_7570000/newsid_7578100/7578168.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>，而[[国际奥委会|国际奥委会]]亦启动了对其年龄问题的调查<ref>{{cite web | language=en | publisher=Times Online | title=International Olympic Committee launches probe into He Kexin's age | url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/olympics/article4583174.ece | author= | date=August 22, 2008 | accessdate=2008-08-24 | archive-date=2008-09-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080906232341/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/olympics/article4583174.ece | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在中國女子體操隊奪得團體冠軍後，一名來自美國的女記者直接質疑何可欣的年齡，何可欣堅稱自己已經16歲<ref>{{cite web | language=zh-hans | publisher=新浪網 | title=何可欣輕鬆化解記者質疑 向全世界展現氣度與智慧 | url=http://news.sina.com/sports/sinacn/406-105-105-125/2008-08-18/13263215784.html | author= | date=2008-08-18 | accessdate=2009-01-02 | archive-date=2008-09-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080926193551/http://news.sina.com/sports/sinacn/406-105-105-125/2008-08-18/13263215784.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

8月21日，国际奥委会发表声明表示目前为止没有证据证明中国女子体操队的选手虚报年龄<ref>{{cite web| language=zh-hans| publisher=体坛网| title=无证据证明中国违规 选手年龄问题暂告段落| url=http://news.titan24.com/titan/1/08-08-22/108226.html| author=| date=2008-08-22| accessdate=2008-08-24| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080826024637/http://news.titan24.com/titan/1/08-08-22/108226.html| archivedate=2008-08-26}}</ref>。中国体育代表团副团长崔大林於24日表示，对于何可欣年龄问题产生误会是由于在转会注册中，出现了年龄的差错<ref>{{cite web | language=zh-hans | publisher=国际在线 | title=中国体操队员年龄误会产生于转会注册中的差错 | url=http://gb.cri.cn/17844/2008/08/24/882s2209306.htm | author= | date=2008-08-24 | accessdate=2008-08-24 | archive-date=2008-08-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080830070504/http://gb.cri.cn/17844/2008/08/24/882s2209306.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。8月25日，有媒體報導國際奧委會重點查何可欣年龄<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hk.news.yahoo.com/article/080824/4/7uy5.html |title=國際奧委會重點查何可欣 |accessdate=2008-08-30 |archive-date=2008-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080828033747/http://hk.news.yahoo.com/article/080824/4/7uy5.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。調查結果於同年10月1日宣佈，國際體操總會最終接納中國提供的文件，證實有關運動員參賽時已年滿16歲，符合參賽資格<ref>[http://appledaily.atnext.com/template/apple/art_main.cfm?iss_id=20081002&sec_id=25391&subsec_id=25392&art_id=11672254 京奧體操虛報年齡案終結] {{Wayback|url=http://appledaily.atnext.com/template/apple/art_main.cfm?iss_id=20081002&sec_id=25391&subsec_id=25392&art_id=11672254 |date=20081005011930 }}．蘋果日報（2008年10月2日）</ref>，顯示何可欣的正確出生日期為1992年1月1日。

